|ical Institute    |                  |                  |unced about 40-60 | 
|                  |                  |                  |grants from $10,00| 
|                  |                  |                  |0 to $75,000 annu-| 
|                  |                  |                  |ally for basic bi-| 
|                  |                  |                  |ology research in | 
|                  |                  |                  |countries of form-| 
|                  |                  |                  |er USSR; equal am-| 
|                  |                  |                  |ount for collabor-| 
|                  |                  |                  |ation with the We-| 
|                  |                  |                  |st                | 
